  {
    title: "Alta Terapêutica",
    desc: "Fortaleceremos sua capacidade de lidar com suas questões de forma independente.<br>Por fim, faremos uma recapitulação do que foi alcançado, de modo a facilitar a manutenção do progresso a longo prazo.",
    align: "left",
    pinClass: "card1",
    width: "62%", 
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none"><rect x="1.2627" y="1.00049" width="46" height="46" rx="23" fill="#F9F2EC"></rect><rect x="1.2627" y="1.00049" width="46" height="46" rx="23" stroke="#F9F2EC"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M19.7625 7.12549C14.5848 7.12549 10.3875 11.3228 10.3875 16.5005C10.3875 19.3827 11.6884 21.96 13.7324 23.6789C10.5798 25.4267 8.27491 28.5036 7.59438 32.1533C7.42517 33.0607 7.59562 33.961 8.11173 34.6795C8.62897 35.3996 9.43025 35.8487 10.3533 35.9681C11.9929 36.1803 14.8328 36.3755 19.7627 36.3755C21.5918 36.3755 23.1332 36.3486 24.4323 36.3039C23.5851 34.646 23.1375 32.7876 23.1375 30.9005C23.1375 29.7307 23.1949 28.68 23.2643 27.8348C23.4311 25.8047 24.5928 23.7534 26.6769 22.8314C28.2044 21.164 29.1375 18.9417 29.1375 16.5005C29.1375 11.3228 24.9402 7.12549 19.7625 7.12549ZM33.2627 24.3755C31.116 24.3755 29.6249 24.4803 28.5933 24.6138C26.7348 24.8544 25.6435 26.3562 25.5069 28.019C25.4416 28.8146 25.3877 29.8029 25.3877 30.9005C25.3877 34.335 27.2021 37.5912 30.3153 39.1935C31.2222 39.6602 32.3209 40.1255 33.2627 40.1255C34.2045 40.1255 35.3031 39.6602 36.21 39.1935C39.3233 37.5912 41.1377 34.335 41.1377 30.9005C41.1377 29.8029 41.0838 28.8146 41.0184 28.019C40.8819 26.3562 39.7905 24.8544 37.9321 24.6138C36.9005 24.4803 35.4094 24.3755 33.2627 24.3755ZM36.8904 27.9419C37.406 28.2885 37.5429 28.9875 37.1963 29.5032L33.6669 34.7532C33.4725 35.0424 33.1548 35.2252 32.807 35.2481C32.4591 35.2709 32.1204 35.1312 31.8897 34.8698L29.4191 32.0698C29.008 31.6039 29.0525 30.893 29.5184 30.4819C29.9843 30.0708 30.6952 30.1152 31.1063 30.5811L32.6127 32.2884L35.3291 28.2478C35.6757 27.7322 36.3747 27.5952 36.8904 27.9419Z" fill="#D94881"></path></svg>`
